            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to an IGBT chip and a back implementation method thereof. The invention provides an IGBT chip and a back implementation method thereof, which achieves the parameter consistency with high-energy hydrogen injection IGBTs at a low cost and reduces the equipment dependence. The IGBT chip comprises a metal layer, a BPSG passivation layer, a POLY layer, a gate oxide, an N+ region and a Pbody region, and further comprises an N- layer, an N buffer layer, an N- substrate and a P+ collector which are arranged in turn from top to bottom, the thickness range of the N- layer is 4-150[mu]m, and the thickness range of the N buffer layer is 5[mu]m-30[mu]m. According to the invention, secondary epitaxy is carried out through an N- single crystal wafer, the epitaxial layer I is N doped (i.e. the N buffer layer), the epitaxial layer II is N- doped, the thinning is ended in the N- substrate when subsequent thinning is performed after the front process of the IGBT is completed, and then P+ is injected to realize an IGBT back structure. Meanwhile, the concentration distribution of the epitaxial N buffer layer is straight, and NN+ junctions with small concentration gradient will be formed under the action of the front thermal process, thereby being conducive to improving the dynamic avalanche ability of the IGBT."
                },
                {
                    "p": "一种IGBT芯片及其背面实现方法。提供了一种用较低成本实现与高能氢注入IGBT的参数一致性，降低了设备依赖性的IGBT芯片及其背面实现方法。包括金属层、BPSG钝化层、POLY层、栅氧化层、N+区和Pbody区，还包括从上到下依次设置的N‑层、N缓冲层、N‑衬底和P+集电极，所述N‑层的厚度范围为4~150um，N缓冲层的厚度范围为5um~30um。本发明通过N‑单晶片二次外延，外延层一为N掺杂（即N缓冲层），外延层二为N‑掺杂，在IGBT正面工艺完成后，进行后续减薄时减薄截至在衬底N‑内，然后注入P+，实现IGBT背面结构。同时，外延N缓冲层浓度分布平直，再加上正面的热过程作用，会形成较小浓度梯度的NN+结，这有利于提高IGBT的动态雪崩能力。"
                }
            ]
